# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# proxy.txt — Proxy list for the go-ingestion pipeline
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Place one proxy per line. Empty lines and lines starting with
# '#' are ignored.
#
# Supported protocols: http, https, socks5
#
# Format:
#   <protocol>://[user:pass@]host:port
#
# Examples:
#   http://user:pass@proxy.example.com:8080
#   http://198.51.100.42:3128
#   https://10.0.0.1:443
#   socks5://127.0.0.1:9050
#
# To use this configuration:
#   cp proxy.txt.example proxy.txt
#   # then populate proxy.txt with real proxies
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
